text.text:
Good coffee, but the food options were limited.  Unfortunately I couldn't make myself understood to the very charming waitress.

The furniture is unique and funky and I love the decorations. I hope they find a way to keep the plastic pants dust free long term. This place has huge potential as a wine bar or club.

The entrance from the station side is a bit hard to find.
